{"title_page": "Slatinka nad Bebravou", "text_new": "{{Infobox settlement\n| name                    = Slatinka nad Bebravou\n| native_name             = \n| other_name              = \n| settlement_type         = Municipality\n<!-- images, nickname, motto -->\n| image_skyline           = \n| image_caption           = \n| image_flag              = \n| image_shield            = \n| motto                   = \n| nickname                = \n| etymology               = \n<!-- location -->\n| subdivision_type        = Country\n| subdivision_name        = Slovakia\n| subdivision_type1       = \n| subdivision_name1       = \n| subdivision_type2       = Region\n| subdivision_name2       = [[Tren\u010d\u00edn Region|Tren\u010d\u00edn]]\n| subdivision_type3       = District\n| subdivision_name3       = [[B\u00e1novce nad Bebravou District|B\u00e1novce nad Bebravou]]\n| subdivision_type4       = \n| subdivision_name4       = \n<!-- maps and coordinates -->\n| image_map               = \n| map_caption             = \n| pushpin_map             = Slovakia Tren\u010d\u00edn Region#Slovakia\n| pushpin_relief          = 1\n| pushpin_map_caption     = Location of Slatinka nad Bebravou in the [[Tren\u010d\u00edn Region]]\n| coordinates             = {{coord|48|51|N|18|15|E|display=inline,title}}\n| coordinates_footnotes   = \n<!-- established -->\n| established_title       = First mentioned\n| established_date        = 1332\n<!-- area -->\n| area_footnotes          = \n| area_total_km2          = 11.527\n| area_total_sq_mi        = \n| area_land_sq_mi         = \n| area_water_sq_mi        = \n<!-- elevation -->\n| elevation_footnotes     = \n| elevation_m             = 275\n| elevation_ft            = \n<!-- population -->\n| population_as_of        = \n| population_footnotes    = \n| population_total        = 507\n| population_density_km2  = auto\n| population_density_sq_mi=\n| population_demonym      = \n<!-- time zone(s) -->\n| timezone1               = \n| utc_offset1             = \n| timezone1_DST           = \n| utc_offset1_DST         = \n<!-- postal codes, area code -->\n| postal_code_type        = Postal code\n| postal_code             = 956 53 (po\u0161ta Slatina nad Bebravou)\n| area_code_type          =  \n| area_code               = 421-38\n| geocode                 = \n| iso_code                = \n| blank_name              = [[Slovak car registration plates|Car plate]]\n| blank_info              = BN\n<!-- website, footnotes -->\n| website                 = [http://slatinkanb.sk  slatinkanb.sk]\n| footnotes               = \n}}\n\n'''Slatinka nad Bebravou''' ({{lang-hu|Als\u00f3szalatna}}) is a [[village]] and [[municipality]] in '''[[B\u00e1novce nad Bebravou District]]''' in the '''[[Tren\u010d\u00edn Region]]''' of north-western '''[[Slovakia]]'''.\n\n==History==\nIn [[history|historical records]] the [[village]] was first mentioned in 1332.\n\n==Geography==\nThe [[municipality]] lies at an [[altitude]] of 275 metres and covers an [[area]] of 11.527&nbsp;km\u00b2. It has a [[population]] of about 507 people.\n\n==External links==\n* [http://slatinkanb.sk Official page]\n*https://web.archive.org/web/20070513023228/http://www.statistics.sk/mosmis/eng/run.html\n\n{{Banovce nad Bebravou District}}\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Villages and municipalities in B\u00e1novce nad Bebravou District]]\n\n\n{{Tren\u010d\u00edn-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n| name                    = Slatinka nad Bebravou\n| native_name             = \n| other_name              = \n| settlement_type         = Municipality\n<!-- images, nickname, motto -->\n| image_skyline           = \n| image_caption           = \n| image_flag              = \n| image_shield            = \n| motto                   = \n| nickname                = \n| etymology               = \n<!-- location -->\n| subdivision_type        = Country\n| subdivision_name        = Slovakia\n| subdivision_type1       = \n| subdivision_name1       = \n| subdivisio